   "source": [
    "# Function Calling vs Agent：深度对比\n",
    "\n",
    "## 核心区别\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. Function Calling（函数调用）\n",
    "- **定义**：LLM的一个特性，允许模型结构化地调用预定义函数\n",
    "- **特点**：单次决策，直接调用，无状态\n",
    "- **流程**：用户输入 → 模型决定调用哪个函数 → 执行函数 → 返回结果\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. Agent（智能体）\n",
    "- **定义**：一个完整的系统，具有推理、规划和执行能力\n",
    "- **特点**：多步推理，迭代执行，可维护状态\n",
    "- **流程**：用户输入 → 思考 → 行动 → 观察 → 再思考 → ... → 最终结果"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "from dotenv import load_dotenv\n",
    "import json\n",
    "from openai import OpenAI\n",
    "from langchain.agents import initialize_agent, Tool, AgentType\n",
    "from langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI\n",
    "\n",
    "# 加载环境变量\n",
    "load_dotenv()\n",
    "os.environ[\"LANGCHAIN_TRACING_V2\"] = \"false\""
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 示例1：Function Calling（简单直接）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 初始化OpenAI客户端\n",
    "client = OpenAI()\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义函数\n",
    "def get_weather(location: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"获取天气信息\"\"\"\n",
    "    weather_data = {\n",
    "        \"北京\": {\"温度\": \"25°C\", \"天气\": \"晴\"},\n",
    "        \"上海\": {\"温度\": \"22°C\", \"天气\": \"多云\"},\n",
    "        \"广州\": {\"温度\": \"28°C\", \"天气\": \"小雨\"}\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    data = weather_data.get(location, {\"温度\": \"未知\", \"天气\": \"未知\"})\n",
    "    return f\"{location}天气：{data['天气']}，温度{data['温度']}\"\n",
    "\n",
    "def calculate(expression: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"计算数学表达式\"\"\"\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        result = eval(expression)\n",
    "        return f\"计算结果：{result}\"\n",
    "    except:\n",
    "        return \"计算错误\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# 定义函数规范\n",
    "tools = [\n",
    "    {\n",
    "        \"type\": \"function\",\n",
    "        \"function\": {\n",
    "            \"name\": \"get_weather\",\n",
    "            \"description\": \"获取指定城市的天气信息\",\n",
    "            \"parameters\": {\n",
    "                \"type\": \"object\",\n",
    "                \"properties\": {\n",
    "                    \"location\": {\n",
    "                        \"type\": \"string\",\n",
    "                        \"description\": \"城市名称\"\n",
    "                    }\n",
    "                },\n",
    "                \"required\": [\"location\"]\n",
    "            }\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    },\n",
    "    {\n",
    "        \"type\": \"function\",\n",
    "        \"function\": {\n",
    "            \"name\": \"calculate\",\n",
    "            \"description\": \"计算数学表达式\",\n",
    "            \"parameters\": {\n",
    "                \"type\": \"object\",\n",
    "                \"properties\": {\n",
    "                    \"expression\": {\n",
    "                        \"type\": \"string\",\n",
    "                        \"description\": \"数学表达式\"\n",
    "                    }\n",
    "                },\n",
    "                \"required\": [\"expression\"]\n",
    "            }\n",
    "        }\n",
    "    }\n",
    "]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Function Calling 示例\n",
    "def function_calling_example(query: str):\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n=== Function Calling 示例 ===\")\n",
    "    print(f\"查询: {query}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 第一次调用：让模型决定调用哪些函数\n",
    "    response = client.chat.completions.create(\n",
    "        model=\"gpt-3.5-turbo\",\n",
    "        messages=[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": query}],\n",
    "        tools=tools,\n",
    "        tool_choice=\"auto\"\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 获取模型的回复\n",
    "    message = response.choices[0].message\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if message.tool_calls:\n",
    "        # 执行函数调用\n",
    "        results = []\n",
    "        for tool_call in message.tool_calls:\n",
    "            function_name = tool_call.function.name\n",
    "            arguments = json.loads(tool_call.function.arguments)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            print(f\"\\n调用函数: {function_name}\")\n",
    "            print(f\"参数: {arguments}\")\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # 执行对应函数\n",
    "            if function_name == \"get_weather\":\n",
    "                result = get_weather(arguments[\"location\"])\n",
    "            elif function_name == \"calculate\":\n",
    "                result = calculate(arguments[\"expression\"])\n",
    "            \n",
    "            print(f\"结果: {result}\")\n",
    "            results.append(result)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 将结果返回给模型生成最终回复\n",
    "        final_response = client.chat.completions.create(\n",
    "            model=\"gpt-3.5-turbo\",\n",
    "            messages=[\n",
    "                {\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": query},\n",
    "                {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": \"\\n\".join(results)}\n",
    "            ]\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        print(f\"\\n最终回复: {final_response.choices[0].message.content}\")\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        print(f\"\\n直接回复: {message.content}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 测试Function Calling\n",
    "function_calling_example(\"北京天气怎么样？\")\n",
    "function_calling_example(\"北京天气怎么样？如果温度超过20度，计算25*4\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 示例2：Agent（智能推理）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Agent 示例\n",
    "def agent_example(query: str):\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n=== Agent 示例 ===\")\n",
    "    print(f\"查询: {query}\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 创建工具\n",
    "    tools = [\n",
    "        Tool(\n",
    "            name=\"Weather\",\n",
    "            func=get_weather,\n",
    "            description=\"获取城市天气信息，输入城市名称\"\n",
    "        ),\n",
    "        Tool(\n",
    "            name=\"Calculator\",\n",
    "            func=calculate,\n",
    "            description=\"计算数学表达式\"\n",
    "        )\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 初始化Agent\n",
    "    llm = ChatOpenAI(temperature=0, model=\"gpt-3.5-turbo\")\n",
    "    agent = initialize_agent(\n",
    "        tools=tools,\n",
    "        llm=llm,\n",
    "        agent=AgentType.ZERO_SHOT_REACT_DESCRIPTION,\n",
    "        verbose=True\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 执行查询\n",
    "    response = agent.invoke({\"input\": query})\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n最终回答: {response['output']}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 测试Agent\n",
    "agent_example(\"北京天气怎么样？\")\n",
    "agent_example(\"北京天气怎么样？如果温度超过20度，计算25*4\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 关键区别对比\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. **执行模式**\n",
    "- **Function Calling**: 一次性决策，同时调用多个函数\n",
    "- **Agent**: 迭代式思考，逐步执行\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. **推理能力**\n",
    "- **Function Calling**: 简单的函数映射\n",
    "- **Agent**: 复杂的逻辑推理（如\"如果温度>20度，则...\"）\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. **错误处理**\n",
    "- **Function Calling**: 需要开发者处理\n",
    "- **Agent**: 可以自主重试和调整策略\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. **状态管理**\n",
    "- **Function Calling**: 无状态\n",
    "- **Agent**: 可以维护对话状态和记忆"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 高级示例：展示Agent的独特能力"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 添加更复杂的工具展示Agent能力\n",
    "def search_knowledge(query: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"搜索知识库\"\"\"\n",
    "    knowledge = {\n",
    "        \"台风\": \"台风是热带气旋的一种，风速超过17.2米/秒\",\n",
    "        \"降雨量\": \"大雨：24小时降雨量25-50mm，暴雨：50-100mm\",\n",
    "        \"温度记录\": \"北京历史最高温度：41.9°C（1999年）\"\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    \n",
    "    for key, value in knowledge.items():\n",
    "        if key in query:\n",
    "            return value\n",
    "    return \"未找到相关信息\"\n",
    "\n",
    "def analyze_data(data: str) -> str:\n",
    "    \"\"\"分析数据\"\"\"\n",
    "    if \"温度\" in data and \"25\" in data:\n",
    "        return \"温度适中，适合户外活动\"\n",
    "    elif \"小雨\" in data:\n",
    "        return \"有降雨，建议携带雨具\"\n",
    "    return \"数据分析完成\"\n",
    "\n",
    "# 创建高级Agent\n",
    "advanced_tools = [\n",
    "    Tool(name=\"Weather\", func=get_weather, description=\"获取天气信息\"),\n",
    "    Tool(name=\"Calculate\", func=calculate, description=\"计算数学表达式\"),\n",
    "    Tool(name=\"Search\", func=search_knowledge, description=\"搜索相关知识\"),\n",
    "    Tool(name=\"Analyze\", func=analyze_data, description=\"分析数据并给出建议\")\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "llm = ChatOpenAI(temperature=0)\n",
    "advanced_agent = initialize_agent(\n",
    "    tools=advanced_tools,\n",
    "    llm=llm,\n",
    "    agent=AgentType.ZERO_SHOT_REACT_DESCRIPTION,\n",
    "    verbose=True\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# 复杂查询示例\n",
    "print(\"\\n=== 复杂Agent推理示例 ===\")\n",
    "complex_query = \"帮我分析北京和广州的天气，如果有降雨告诉我降雨量标准，并给出出行建议\"\n",
    "response = advanced_agent.invoke({\"input\": complex_query})\n",
    "print(f\"\\n最终回答: {response['output']}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 总结：什么时候用什么？\n",
    "\n",
    "### 使用 Function Calling 的场景：\n",
    "1. **简单直接的任务**：如"获取天气"、"设置提醒"\n",
    "2. **确定性流程**：步骤固定，不需要复杂推理\n",
    "3. **低延迟要求**：需要快速响应\n",
    "4. **成本敏感**：减少API调用次数\n",
    "\n",
    "### 使用 Agent 的场景：\n",
    "1. **复杂推理任务**：需要多步思考和条件判断\n",
    "2. **探索性任务**：不确定需要调用哪些工具\n",
    "3. **错误恢复**：需要自动处理错误和重试\n",
    "4. **状态管理**：需要记住之前的交互\n",
    "5. **自主决策**：让AI自主规划执行步骤\n",
    "\n",
    "### 类比理解\n",
    "- **Function Calling** = 遥控器（按哪个按钮执行哪个功能）\n",
    "- **Agent** = 智能助手（告诉目标，自主规划和执行）"
   ]
  }
